tool_description: Get access to hundreds of L2TP and Open VPN Accounts to you for your security or in your next big project. Powered by Turbo VPN, Express VPN, VPN Gate, SurfShark and VPN Book. Suggest more protocols to be added.
name: VPN Accounts
title: VPN Accounts

api_list.name: OVPN From Ip
api_list.description: Get the .ovpn configuration file from the IP Address.
api_list.code:
import requests

url = "https://vpn-accounts.p.rapidapi.com/getOvpnForIp/163.182.174.159"

headers = {
            "X-RapidAPI-Key": "SIGN-UP-FOR-KEY",
            "X-RapidAPI-Host": "vpn-accounts.p.rapidapi.com"
        }

response = requests.get(url, headers=headers)
print(response.json())
